  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe two medical uses of nuclear technology</item>
<item>Explain the origin of biological effects due to nuclear radiation</item>
<item>List common sources of radiation and their effects</item>
<item>Estimate exposure for nuclear radiation using common dosage units</item>
</list></md:abstract>
